      "id": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/recipes/beef-and-yellow-split-pea-stew-with-crispy-potatoes",
      "url": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/recipes/beef-and-yellow-split-pea-stew-with-crispy-potatoes",
      "title": "Beef and yellow split pea stew with crispy potatoes",
      "content_html": "<h1 style=\"text-align:center;font-family:sans-serif;\">Beef and yellow split pea stew with crispy potatoes</h1>\n        <br>\n        <img src=\"https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/beef-and-yellow-split-pea-stew-with-crispy-potatoes.webp\" style=\"text-align:center;\"/>\n        <br>\n        <p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;>To me, this dish represents an Iranian take on the classic meat and potato comfort dish, with a few unique ingredients, of course! Persian dried limes, or limu om\u0101ni, provide a bold, tangy citrus taste with deep, earthy, fermented undertones.</p>",
      "image": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/beef-and-yellow-split-pea-stew-with-crispy-potatoes.webp",
      "date_published": "2026-04-04T00:00:00+00:00Z",
      "language": "en"
