    {
      "id": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/recipes/soy-and-mirin-tuna-on-soba-noodles",
      "url": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/recipes/soy-and-mirin-tuna-on-soba-noodles",
      "title": "Soy & mirin tuna on soba noodles",
      "content_html": "<h1 style=\"text-align:center;font-family:sans-serif;\">Soy & mirin tuna on soba noodles</h1>\n        <br>\n        <img src=\"https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/soy-and-mirin-tuna-on-soba-noodles.webp\" style=\"text-align:center;\"/>\n        <br>\n        <p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;>Soba means 'buckwheat' in Japenese and there are two types of soba noodles - the normal dark brown noodle with the natural colour of buckwheat and the green-coloured 'green tea' soba. You can use either, but the green tea version looks very pretty and gives a fresher, lighter taste to the dish.</p>",
      "image": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/soy-and-mirin-tuna-on-soba-noodles.webp",
      "date_published": "2026-03-30T00:00:00+00:00Z",
      "language": "en"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/recipes/harissa-chicken-tomato-and-olive-pasties",
      "url": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/recipes/harissa-chicken-tomato-and-olive-pasties",
      "title": "Harissa chicken, tomato and olive pasties",
      "content_html": "<h1 style=\"text-align:center;font-family:sans-serif;\">Harissa chicken, tomato and olive pasties</h1>\n        <br>\n        <img src=\"https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/harissa-chicken-tomato-and-olive-pasties.webp\" style=\"text-align:center;\"/>\n        <br>\n        <p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;>It\u2019s a sad day when there\u2019s not a jar of harissa in my fridge; it\u2019s such a versatile seasoning. Here, it really brings the filling ingredients together and when I bake these I love the sight of its bright red oil escaping from any tiny crack in the pastry \u2013 it\u2019s a sign of promising things to come.</p>",
      "image": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/harissa-chicken-tomato-and-olive-pasties.webp",
      "date_published": "2026-03-29T00:00:00+00:00Z",
      "language": "en"
    }
  ]
